    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>German spiked helmets before and early during WWI. They were made ​​of pressed leather, pressed horsehair, or metal. A metal spike or sphere was mounted on the top of the helmet.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
